OCI image-spec JSON Schemas — vendored verbatim for Step 9B schema-validity tests.

Upstream:  https://github.com/opencontainers/image-spec/tree/v1.1.1/schema
Tag:       v1.1.1
Commit:    147f9c13cedb47a0c4d9a11a222961073d585877
Retrieved: 2026-06-06

Files copied verbatim (do not edit — re-fetch from the pinned commit to bump):

  config-schema.json          image config        (Stevedore.Config emits this)
  content-descriptor.json     descriptor          (manifest config/layers/subject)
  defs-descriptor.json        shared defs: mediaType, digest, urls, annotations
  defs.json                   shared defs: int64, mapStringString, ...
  image-index-schema.json     image index         (multi-arch + referrers index)
  image-layout-schema.json    oci-layout marker    (kept for completeness)
  image-manifest-schema.json  image manifest      (Stevedore.Image emits this)

These are draft-04 schemas that $ref each other by bare filename. The resolver in
test/support/schema_validator.ex maps each cross-file $ref back to the matching
file here by basename.

Bump procedure: re-fetch the seven files verbatim from a new pinned tag, then update
the Tag/Commit/Retrieved lines above. From this directory:

  TAG=v1.1.1   # the image-spec tag to pin
  base="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/opencontainers/image-spec/$TAG/schema"
  for f in config-schema content-descriptor defs-descriptor defs \
           image-index-schema image-layout-schema image-manifest-schema; do
    curl -fsSL "$base/$f.json" -o "$f.json"
  done
